description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Central Food Production Unit Distribution Porter, Band 2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(Full /Part Time hours)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lakeside, UHW&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity is available to join the Commercial Services team within Capital, Estates &amp; Facilities in the Central Food Production Unit, University Hospital of Wales Heath, Cardiff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for motivated and enthusiastic staff colleagues with a flexible approach to work and to join our Commercial Services catering team. Candidates should be committed to maintaining high service standards and possess relevant food hygiene certification. Applicants should have a track record of working in catering as well as distributing and stock control. Working as part of a team or on their own together with a high commitment to excellent customer care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will need to be able to work on their own initiative or as part of the catering team in the patient food production area, have the ability to adapt to a changing service environment within a high profile UHB location and be required to complete workloads according to schedules and service needs. Together with ensuring the day to day safe delivery of a quality focused service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will share and be able to demonstrate our values that include caring for the people we serve and the people we work with, we trust one another, respect each other, take personal responsibility, treat people with kindness and we act with integrity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you feel you have the ability, appetite and ambition required to assist in delivering our services, we would welcome your application.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 9th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
